data.description: PROBATE PROPERTY WITH GREAT POTENTIAL! Corner home located on a street with a cul-de-sac is located in a gated community.  The home needs some TLC in regards to a good cleaning! There is laminate wood flooring in the living area, a cozy fireplace, ceramic tile in the kitchen & eating area, a breakfast bar and carpeting in the bedrooms.  In front there is a covered porch and in back a cozy yard has a covered patio surrounded by a privacy fence. This could be a great investment property or a great homestead! To get an idea of the potential of the home, visit MLS # 1092094 to see pictures and get an idea.
